{"tid":1950793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毋忘初心，we will be back soon","createTime":"2020-03-30T14:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T10:58:33.000Z","uid":50306,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5098ff43895527cc73b906d5c4ea13ec119389d8","tid":1950793,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"是咁的，眾所周知小弟係一個無金主支持，無政治背景既連登仔，係對上兩次遊行（實際只係搞左一次）都係自己同埋teammates夾錢，而係「廢府。肺話」集會亦都首次網上眾籌經費，係度都好多謝各位手足相信我地，奈何集會因為疫情問題取消，但我地經費係繼續沿用落去<br />\n<br />\n我地眾籌截至現時為止籌左25785.86 HKD (gogetfunding 24916HKD / buymeacoffee 105 USD)，扣除手續費我地實收24843.25 HKD<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n聽日就係831 7個月，呢啲日子我地永遠都唔會忘記<br />\n過去呢幾個月因為疫情問題，令到抗爭活動少左好多，但小弟相信手足們係無忘記到佢地既初心，有繼續為抗爭做好準備，係呢度想同大家分享一句我好鐘意既句子：<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，從來都只係你一個人既時代革命 &mdash; by 文宣巴<br />\n<br />\n而我地團隊都會應承大家，毋忘初心，we will be back soon.<br />\n<br />\n以此post為證<br />\n<br />\nChannel：<a href=\"https://t.me/fivednotonel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffivednotonel&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2cv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=60beeae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fivednotonel</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEcHP7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEcHP7n.jpg&h=79237d35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0e2ba539589e70a217f3716fdf25534159c7758","tid":1950793,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05eef1c51c8d6005d0cef311e64f4e71695c1da4","tid":1950793,"uid":206421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa78dc25144a4861693a8cfa3a0d3f70ec8ecfe1","tid":1950793,"uid":134483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re